fields.name: DefaultEncryptionScope
fields.description: Default the container to use specified encryption scope for all writes.

fields.name: Deleted
fields.description: Indicates whether the blob container was deleted.

fields.name: DenyEncryptionScopeOverride
fields.description: Block override of encryption scope from the container default.

fields.name: EnableNfsV3AllSquash
fields.description: Enable NFSv3 all squash on blob container.

fields.name: EnableNfsV3RootSquash
fields.description: Enable NFSv3 root squash on blob container.

fields.name: HasImmutabilityPolicy
fields.description: The hasImmutabilityPolicy public property is set to true by SRP if ImmutabilityPolicy has been created for this container. The hasImmutabilityPolicy public property is set to false by SRP if ImmutabilityPolicy has not been created for this container.

fields.name: HasLegalHold
fields.description: The hasLegalHold public property is set to true by SRP if there are at least one existing tag. The hasLegalHold public property is set to false by SRP if all existing legal hold tags are cleared out. There can be a maximum of 1000 blob containers with hasLegalHold=true for a given account.

fields.name: ImmutabilityPolicy
fields.description: The ImmutabilityPolicy property of the container.

fields.name: ImmutableStorageWithVersioning
fields.description: The object level immutability property of the container. The property is immutable and can only be set to true at the container creation time. Existing containers must undergo a migration process.

fields.name: LastModifiedTime
fields.description: Returns the date and time the container was last modified.

fields.name: LeaseDuration
fields.description: Specifies whether the lease on a container is of infinite or fixed duration, only when the container is leased.

fields.name: LeaseStatus
fields.description: The lease status of the container.

fields.name: LegalHold
fields.description: The LegalHold property of the container.

fields.name: Metadata
fields.description: A name-value pair to associate with the container as metadata.

fields.name: PublicAccess
fields.description: Specifies whether data in the container may be accessed publicly and the level of access.

fields.name: RemainingRetentionDays
fields.description: Remaining retention days for soft deleted blob container.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: The version of the deleted blob container.
